Package: aadk
Version: @VERSION@
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Jaron Rosenau <jaron@rosenau.info>
Depends: bash, libgtk-4-1
Recommends: openjdk-21-jre | openjdk-17-jre
Description: AADK Android DevKit suite
 AADK provides a GTK UI plus gRPC services for toolchain,
 project, build, targets, workflows, and job monitoring.
